OL,3,CUpdate to be announced on probe into
OL,4,Cclerical sex abuse ` Taoiseach
OL,6,FThere is set to be an update on
OL,7,Fprogress around establishing a
OL,8,Fcommission of investigation into
OL,9,Fclerical sex abuse, the Taoiseach has
OL,10,Findicated.
OL,12,FSimon Harris was speaking amid calls
OL,13,Ffor corporal punishment in schools to
OL,14,Fbe included in the investigation.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday night, RTE screened a
OL,17,Fdocumentary focusing on the use of
OL,18,Fcorporal punishment in Irish schools
OL,19,Ffrom the middle of the 20th century.
