OL,3,CUpdate to be announced on probe into
OL,4,Cclerical sex abuse ` Taoiseach
OL,6,FMr Harris described the evidence on
OL,7,Fthe historic punishment inflicted on
OL,8,Fchildren in schools as "harrowing
OL,9,Fviewing".
OL,11,F"I commend all of those who told their
OL,12,Fstories," he said.
OL,14,F"I expect there will shortly be an
OL,15,Fupdate to the Government on the
OL,16,Fprogress of establishing a Commission
OL,17,Fof Investigation into clerical sex
OL,18,Fabuse."
