OL,3,CUpdate to be announced on probe into
OL,4,Cclerical sex abuse ` Taoiseach
OL,6,FMr Harris said a scoping inquiry ahead
OL,7,Fof the commission of investigation
OL,8,F"exposed a culture of violence, of
OL,9,Fcalculated cruelty and the abuse of
OL,10,Fpower that victimised and terrorised
OL,11,Fgenerations of Irish children who
OL,12,Fstill bear the wounds and have for all
OL,13,Fof their lives".
OL,15,F"It is an unbearable burden which we
OL,16,Fmust help lift," he said.
