OL,6,F"I have listened carefully to
OL,7,Fsurvivors tonight about expanding the
OL,8,Finquiry and will now reflect on the
OL,9,Frequest as their voices cannot, and
OL,10,Fmust not, be ignored or unheard.
OL,12,F"This process cannot be rushed because
OL,13,Fit has to be right, and it has to
OL,14,Frespect the wishes of the victims who
OL,15,Fcame forward.
